### Proposed Resolution: Add "Container Security Hardening" section to infrastructure_as_code: (1) hadolint in CI for Dockerfile linting; (2) kube-bench for Kubernetes CIS compliance; (3) seccomp profile examples; (4) Pod Security Standards configuration; (5) read-only filesystem pattern with explicit tmpfs mounts. Triggers: "container hardening", "CIS benchmarks", "Docker security".
### Cross-Phase Impact: Phase 4 security_audit covers application-level security but not infrastructure-level container configuration security. Phase 5.5 has no container runtime security monitoring.

